Pet Camera Requirements:

Hardware:
Camera - High resolution with night vision capabilities, continuous video capture
Connectivity - Ethernet or Wifi connection via Raspberry Pi
Cloud Storage - Upload videos using cloud services (?)

Software/User Experience:
Yolov8 Model - Train model and deploy onto a raspberry pi for real-time object analysis. Model should be trained for pet activity including common household pets.
Notification System - Mobile app that can receive notification using a push notification service (maybe Firebase ?)
Alert Settings - User can choose what activities to be alerted from & input any health/behavior concerns to watch for. They can choose to receive push notifications. 
Real time feed - Application allows user to view the pet footage in real-time remotely.
Stored footage - Application stores footage based on user settings and storage configuration.
 

 
